lines.text: i set out on the road
looking for a pot of gold
things got bad and things got worse
i guess you'd know the tune
i rode in on the greyhound
i'll be walking out if i go
must be seven months or more
i ran out of time and money
looks like they took my friend
said i was on my way
ran out of songs to play
i came into town a one night stand
looks like my plans fell through
if i only had a dollar
and every time i've had to play
you know i'd catch the next
train back to where i live
